snippet.title: I Just Want to be Single!! Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The anti-dating sim where you don't want to date! Play as a socially awkward fem-nb protagonist! Escape cute waifus and navigate your way out of romantic conversations to befriend them instead!

WISHLIST ON STEAM NOW:
